1
00:00:07,583 --> 00:00:08,583
- KATARA: Water.

2
00:00:09,583 --> 00:00:10,583
Earth.

3
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:12,500
Fire.

4
00:00:13,542 --> 00:00:14,542
Air.

5
00:00:16,083 --> 00:00:20,125
Long ago, the four nations
lived together in harmony.

6
00:00:20,166 --> 00:00:23,208
Then, everything changed
when the Fire Nation attacked.

7
00:00:24,625 --> 00:00:27,208
Only the Avatar,
master of all four elements,

8
00:00:27,250 --> 00:00:28,792
could stop them.

9
00:00:28,834 --> 00:00:30,917
But when the world
needed him most, he vanished.

10
00:00:32,250 --> 00:00:34,417
A hundred years passed,
and my brother and I discovered

11
00:00:34,458 --> 00:00:37,625
the new Avatar,
an Airbender named Aang.

12
00:00:37,667 --> 00:00:39,959
And although
his airbending skills are great,

13
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,375
he has a lot to learn before
he's ready to save anyone.

14
00:00:42,417 --> 00:00:43,875
- Ugh!

15
00:00:43,917 --> 00:00:46,792
- KATARA: But I believe
Aang can save the world.

16
00:00:46,834 --> 00:00:50,333
♪

17
00:00:55,333 --> 00:00:57,709
- AANG: There's a man living
at the Eastern Air Temple.

18
00:00:57,750 --> 00:01:00,750
He says he can teach me
to control the Avatar State.

19
00:01:00,792 --> 00:01:05,500
- In the Avatar State,
you are at your most powerful.

20
00:01:05,542 --> 00:01:08,959
But you are also
at your most vulnerable.

21
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,250
- What do you mean?

22
00:01:10,291 --> 00:01:12,959
- If you are killed
in the Avatar State,

23
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,375
the reincarnation
cycle will be broken,

24
00:01:16,417 --> 00:01:19,667
and the Avatar
will cease to exist.

25
00:01:19,709 --> 00:01:21,583
- What's happening?

26
00:01:21,625 --> 00:01:25,166
- You are going through
a metamorphosis, my nephew.

27
00:01:25,208 --> 00:01:29,834
- The Dai Li remains loyal
to you, Long Feng, sir.

28
00:01:29,875 --> 00:01:31,083
- Hello?

29
00:01:33,709 --> 00:01:34,625
[screams]

30
00:01:34,667 --> 00:01:36,166
- It is with
the highest honor

31
00:01:36,208 --> 00:01:38,041
that I welcome
the Kyoshi Warriors.

32
00:01:38,083 --> 00:01:41,041
- We are the Earth King's
humble servants.

33
00:01:42,792 --> 00:01:51,625
♪

34
00:01:51,667 --> 00:01:55,041
- ZUKO:
[yawning]

35
00:01:55,083 --> 00:01:57,083
What's that smell?

36
00:01:57,125 --> 00:02:02,000
- It's jook. I'm sure
you wouldn't like it.

37
00:02:02,041 --> 00:02:03,667
- [inhaling]

38
00:02:03,709 --> 00:02:07,166
Actually, it smells delicious.
I'd love a bowl, Uncle.

39
00:02:09,125 --> 00:02:13,875
- Now that your fever is gone,
you seem different somehow.

40
00:02:13,917 --> 00:02:15,709
- It's a new day.

41
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:17,792
We've got a new apartment,
new furniture,

42
00:02:17,834 --> 00:02:20,291
and today's the grand opening
of your new tea shop.

43
00:02:20,333 --> 00:02:21,709
Things are looking
up, Uncle.

44
00:02:21,750 --> 00:02:23,583
[sipping liquid]

45
00:02:28,208 --> 00:02:30,250
- You haven't seen your
Dad in over two years.

46
00:02:30,291 --> 00:02:31,875
You must be so excited.

47
00:02:31,917 --> 00:02:33,417
- [retches]

48
00:02:33,458 --> 00:02:36,834
I know I should be, but I just
feel sick to my stomach.

49
00:02:36,875 --> 00:02:40,250
- Don't be nervous, he's gonna
be so happy to see you.

50
00:02:40,291 --> 00:02:41,458
- So what about you?

51
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:43,083
Are you nervous
to meet this Guru?

52
00:02:43,125 --> 00:02:44,458
- Not at all.

53
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,375
I'm ready to master
the Avatar State.

54
00:02:46,417 --> 00:02:47,917
I'll do whatever
it takes.

55
00:02:50,208 --> 00:02:51,542
See you in a week.

56
00:02:51,583 --> 00:02:53,083
Yip! Yip!

57
00:02:55,875 --> 00:02:57,583
- [heavy sigh]

58
00:02:57,625 --> 00:03:00,625
♪

59
00:03:09,500 --> 00:03:10,959
- Sokka, good to see you.
- WARRIORS: [laughing]

60
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:14,000
♪

61
00:03:21,083 --> 00:03:27,291
♪

62
00:03:28,250 --> 00:03:30,542
♪

63
00:03:30,583 --> 00:03:32,583
- Sokka.

64
00:03:32,625 --> 00:03:34,542
- Hi, Dad.

65
00:03:34,583 --> 00:03:40,000
♪

66
00:03:40,041 --> 00:03:42,208
- Look, Bosco,

67
00:03:42,250 --> 00:03:45,291
the Kyoshi Warriors
are here to protect us.

68
00:03:45,333 --> 00:03:47,458
Aren't you excited?

69
00:03:47,500 --> 00:03:49,375
- [yawning]

70
00:03:49,417 --> 00:03:50,959
- It's been a difficult
week for me.

71
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:54,291
My most trusted advisor,
Long Feng, and his Dai Li agents

72
00:03:54,333 --> 00:03:57,083
tried to take control
of Ba Sing Se from me.

73
00:03:57,125 --> 00:03:58,542
- It's terrible
when you can't trust

74
00:03:58,583 --> 00:04:00,250
the people who are
closest to you.

75
00:04:00,291 --> 00:04:02,166
- But there is good news.

76
00:04:02,208 --> 00:04:06,125
As we speak, the Council of Five
is meeting to plan an invasion

77
00:04:06,166 --> 00:04:10,500
of The Fire Nation this summer--
on the day of a solar eclipse.

78
00:04:10,542 --> 00:04:11,959
- Really?

79
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:15,542
Now that sounds like a
fascinating and brilliant plan.

80
00:04:21,125 --> 00:04:22,458
- General Fong's base

81
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:25,000
will serve as the launching
point for the attack.

82
00:04:25,041 --> 00:04:28,667
In exactly two months,
the Army and Navy will invade

83
00:04:28,709 --> 00:04:31,917
the Fire Nation
on The Day of Black Sun.

84
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:35,458
- Or we could send in
Momo to do some damage.

85
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,792
[laughing]
'cause the...

86
00:04:37,834 --> 00:04:39,166
Sorry.

87
00:04:41,083 --> 00:04:42,667
- [screeching]

88
00:04:42,709 --> 00:04:45,125
- All we need is
the Earth King's seal

89
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:46,583
in order to execute
the plan.

90
00:04:49,375 --> 00:04:51,083
- I'll get these scrolls
to him right away.

91
00:04:51,125 --> 00:04:54,291
Thank you, General How.

92
00:04:54,333 --> 00:04:55,834
- APPA:
[grunting]

93
00:04:55,875 --> 00:04:58,875
♪

94
00:05:10,166 --> 00:05:11,750
- Um, Hello?

95
00:05:14,166 --> 00:05:15,750
You're Guru Pathik, right?

96
00:05:15,792 --> 00:05:18,041
The person who attached
the note to Appa's horn?

97
00:05:18,083 --> 00:05:19,750
- Indeed.

98
00:05:19,792 --> 00:05:22,333
I was a spiritual brother
of your people,

99
00:05:22,375 --> 00:05:25,667
and a personal friend
of Monk Gyatso.

100
00:05:25,709 --> 00:05:27,667
- In your note, you said
you could teach me

101
00:05:27,709 --> 00:05:30,000
to gain control
of the Avatar State.

102
00:05:30,041 --> 00:05:31,500
How?

103
00:05:31,542 --> 00:05:33,834
- You must gain balance
within yourself

104
00:05:33,875 --> 00:05:36,959
before you can bring
balance to the world.

105
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:40,208
And the first step to gaining
balance begins with this.

106
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:41,500
Drink up.

107
00:05:43,208 --> 00:05:44,917
- [sipping, spitting]

108
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,041
Ugh!

109
00:05:46,083 --> 00:05:49,000
It tastes like onion
and banana juice!

110
00:05:49,041 --> 00:05:50,375
- That's because it is.

111
00:05:50,417 --> 00:05:52,667
[slurping]
Yum! Yum!

112
00:05:56,458 --> 00:05:58,625
- I believe we need
to go right!

113
00:05:58,667 --> 00:06:00,250
- What are you
talking about?

114
00:06:00,291 --> 00:06:02,417
The Bei Fong Estate's
this way.

115
00:06:02,458 --> 00:06:04,375
- I'm quite certain
you're mistaken.

116
00:06:04,417 --> 00:06:06,041
- [loud banging]

117
00:06:06,083 --> 00:06:08,333
Hey, can you two old ladies quit
your bickering for a second?

118
00:06:08,375 --> 00:06:10,750
I gotta go to the bathroom!

119
00:06:10,792 --> 00:06:12,959
- Oh...uh...

120
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,500
Okay, but make it quick.

121
00:06:15,542 --> 00:06:18,083
- What's wrong with you?!

122
00:06:18,125 --> 00:06:20,709
- Oh, very sneaky, Toph!

123
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:24,041
Nice try,
but you can't trick me.

124
00:06:24,083 --> 00:06:27,291
- Let me outta here,
so I can kick both your butts!

125
00:06:27,333 --> 00:06:28,917
- Quit your banging!

126
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,875
You might think you're
the greatest Earthbender

127
00:06:30,917 --> 00:06:34,417
in the world, but even
you can't bend metal.

128
00:06:35,875 --> 00:06:44,583
- ♪

129
00:06:44,625 --> 00:06:46,542
- We have been
presented with

130
00:06:46,583 --> 00:06:48,458
an extraordinary
opportunity, girls.

131
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:49,625
- Mai finally gets
to wear makeup

132
00:06:49,667 --> 00:06:51,750
that's not totally
depressing?

133
00:06:51,792 --> 00:06:53,166
- Ha. Ha.

134
00:06:53,208 --> 00:06:57,959
- I'm talking about conquering
the whole Earth Kingdom.

135
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,792
For a hundred years the Fire
Nation has hammered away

136
00:07:00,834 --> 00:07:03,583
at Ba Sing Se
from the outside.

137
00:07:03,625 --> 00:07:08,333
But now we are on the inside,
and we can take it by ourselves.

138
00:07:08,375 --> 00:07:12,875
- Gosh, you're so confident.
I really admire that about you.

139
00:07:12,917 --> 00:07:14,959
- From the inside, we're
in perfect position

140
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:18,208
to organize a coup
and overthrow the Earth King.

141
00:07:18,250 --> 00:07:20,667
The key is the Dai Li.

142
00:07:20,709 --> 00:07:24,500
Whoever controls the Dai Li,
controls Ba Sing Se.

143
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,750
- In order to master
the Avatar State,

144
00:07:31,792 --> 00:07:35,041
you must open
all the chakras.

145
00:07:35,083 --> 00:07:39,166
Aang, tell me everything
you know about chakras.

146
00:07:39,208 --> 00:07:40,959
- What are chakras?

147
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,834
- Oh, I see.

148
00:07:42,875 --> 00:07:46,375
I guess we'll start
with the basics.

149
00:07:46,417 --> 00:07:48,041
The water flows
through this creek

150
00:07:48,083 --> 00:07:51,500
much like the energy flows
through your body.

151
00:07:51,542 --> 00:07:53,709
As you see there
are several pools

152
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:56,625
where the water swirls
around before flowing on.

153
00:07:56,667 --> 00:08:00,166
These pools are
like our chakras.

154
00:08:00,208 --> 00:08:03,709
- So, chakras are pools of
spiraling energy in our bodies?

155
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:07,000
- Exactly. If nothing
else were around,

156
00:08:07,041 --> 00:08:09,792
this creek would
flow pure and clear.

157
00:08:09,834 --> 00:08:12,166
However, life is messy,

158
00:08:12,208 --> 00:08:14,291
and things tend
to fall in the creek,

159
00:08:14,333 --> 00:08:16,500
and then what happens?

160
00:08:16,542 --> 00:08:19,083
- The creek can't flow?
- Yes.

161
00:08:19,125 --> 00:08:22,750
But if we open the paths
between the pools...

162
00:08:22,792 --> 00:08:24,500
- The energy flows!

163
00:08:24,542 --> 00:08:26,750
- [water gurgling]

164
00:08:29,834 --> 00:08:32,709
- There are seven chakras
that go up the body.

165
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:35,125
Each pool of energy
has a purpose,

166
00:08:35,166 --> 00:08:39,041
and can be blocked by a
specific kind of emotional muck.

167
00:08:39,083 --> 00:08:43,709
Be warned--opening the chakras
is an intense experience,

168
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:45,750
and once you begin
this process,

169
00:08:45,792 --> 00:08:49,500
you cannot stop until
all seven are open.

170
00:08:49,542 --> 00:08:51,000
Are you ready?

171
00:08:53,333 --> 00:08:55,041
- I'll do whatever it takes.

172
00:08:55,083 --> 00:08:57,750
- First we will open
the Earth chakra,

173
00:08:57,792 --> 00:09:00,250
located at the base
of the spine.

174
00:09:00,291 --> 00:09:04,417
It deals with survival
and is blocked by fear.

175
00:09:04,458 --> 00:09:06,250
What are you
most afraid of?

176
00:09:06,291 --> 00:09:07,834
- [dramatic music]

177
00:09:07,875 --> 00:09:10,333
- Let your fears
become clear to you.

178
00:09:10,375 --> 00:09:13,083
- [dramatic music]

179
00:09:13,125 --> 00:09:15,125
- [screaming]

180
00:09:20,250 --> 00:09:21,583
- [dramatic music]

181
00:09:21,625 --> 00:09:23,750
- [screaming]

182
00:09:23,792 --> 00:09:26,959
- GURU: Aang, your vision
is not real.

183
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,625
You are concerned
for your survival,

184
00:09:29,667 --> 00:09:32,166
but you must surrender
those fears.

185
00:09:32,208 --> 00:09:36,000
Let your fears
flow down the creek.

186
00:09:36,041 --> 00:09:39,709
- ♪

187
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:42,375
- You have opened
your Earth chakra.

188
00:09:42,417 --> 00:09:43,792
- Whew.

189
00:09:45,959 --> 00:09:48,500
- [water cascading]

190
00:09:48,542 --> 00:09:51,792
- ♪

191
00:09:51,834 --> 00:09:54,417
- Next is the...
- Water chakra?

192
00:09:54,458 --> 00:09:55,834
- Brilliant!

193
00:09:55,875 --> 00:09:59,166
Maybe one day you
will be a Guru, too.

194
00:09:59,208 --> 00:10:04,083
This chakra deals with pleasure,
and is blocked by guilt.

195
00:10:04,125 --> 00:10:09,625
Now, look at all the guilt
which burdens you so.

196
00:10:09,667 --> 00:10:12,083
What do you blame
yourself for?

197
00:10:12,125 --> 00:10:16,083
- ♪

198
00:10:16,125 --> 00:10:18,000
- AANG:
I ran away.

199
00:10:18,041 --> 00:10:21,041
♪

200
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:30,959
- I hurt all
of those people.

201
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:34,625
- Accept the reality that
these things happened,

202
00:10:34,667 --> 00:10:39,125
but do not let them cloud
and poison your energy.

203
00:10:39,166 --> 00:10:42,583
If you are to be a positive
influence on the world,

204
00:10:42,625 --> 00:10:45,667
you need to
forgive yourself.

205
00:10:45,709 --> 00:10:50,750
- ♪

206
00:10:50,792 --> 00:10:54,834
- This bay leads directly to
the outskirts of Ba Sing Se.

207
00:10:54,875 --> 00:10:56,625
We've been using
these tangle mines

208
00:10:56,667 --> 00:10:59,875
to stop the Fire Nation
ships from getting through.

209
00:10:59,917 --> 00:11:03,792
- Your father invented
tangle mines, himself.

210
00:11:03,834 --> 00:11:06,458
- Destructive,
buoyant, and...

211
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:07,542
[sniffing]

212
00:11:07,583 --> 00:11:09,333
[gasps]

213
00:11:09,375 --> 00:11:10,917
...terrible smelling!

214
00:11:10,959 --> 00:11:12,333
- Very perceptive.

215
00:11:12,375 --> 00:11:15,417
The mines are filled with
skunk-fish and seaweed.

216
00:11:15,458 --> 00:11:17,667
When a ship
detonates the mine,

217
00:11:17,709 --> 00:11:19,667
the seaweed tangles
up the propeller,

218
00:11:19,709 --> 00:11:23,709
and the foul smell forces
people to abandon the ship.

219
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:26,709
I call it
the stink n' sink.

220
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:29,959
- [laughing]
Good one, Dad!

221
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,875
- You are definitely
your father's son.

222
00:11:32,917 --> 00:11:36,583
- Hakoda, our scouts have
spotted four Fire Nation ships.

223
00:11:36,625 --> 00:11:38,792
- Bato, get these
mines loaded up.

224
00:11:38,834 --> 00:11:41,291
The rest of you men,
prepare for battle.

225
00:11:43,542 --> 00:11:45,583
- Um, what should
I do, Dad?

226
00:11:45,625 --> 00:11:47,041
- Aren't you listening?

227
00:11:47,083 --> 00:11:49,792
I said the rest of you men
get ready for battle.

228
00:11:49,834 --> 00:11:58,542
♪

229
00:11:58,583 --> 00:12:02,083
- Who thought when we came
to this city as refugees,

230
00:12:02,125 --> 00:12:05,583
that I'd end up
owning my own tea shop.

231
00:12:05,625 --> 00:12:10,500
Follow your passion, Zuko,
and life will reward you.

232
00:12:10,542 --> 00:12:12,417
- Congratulations, Uncle.

233
00:12:12,458 --> 00:12:14,542
- I'm very thankful.

234
00:12:14,583 --> 00:12:16,375
- You deserve it.

235
00:12:16,417 --> 00:12:19,291
The Jasmine Dragon will be
the best tea shop in the city.

236
00:12:19,333 --> 00:12:22,375
- No, I'm thankful
because you decided

237
00:12:22,417 --> 00:12:25,041
to share this special
day with me.

238
00:12:25,083 --> 00:12:27,792
It means more
than you know.

239
00:12:29,750 --> 00:12:31,458
- Now let's make these
people some tea.

240
00:12:33,417 --> 00:12:36,959
- Yes, let's make
some tea!

241
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:40,834
♪

242
00:12:40,875 --> 00:12:45,041
- Third is the Fire chakra,
located in the stomach.

243
00:12:45,083 --> 00:12:46,917
- My Fire chakra would
like to eat something

244
00:12:46,959 --> 00:12:48,709
other than onion-
banana juice.

245
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:50,125
- [chuckling]

246
00:12:50,166 --> 00:12:52,959
Good one. Moving on.

247
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:57,875
This chakra deals with will
power and is blocked by shame.

248
00:12:57,917 --> 00:13:00,834
What are you ashamed of?

249
00:13:00,875 --> 00:13:03,834
What are your biggest
disappointments in yourself?

250
00:13:03,875 --> 00:13:08,250
♪

251
00:13:08,291 --> 00:13:10,542
- I'm never gonna
fire bend again.

252
00:13:10,583 --> 00:13:12,000
I can't.

253
00:13:12,041 --> 00:13:13,917
- You will never
find balance,

254
00:13:13,959 --> 00:13:17,041
if you deny this
part of your life.

255
00:13:17,083 --> 00:13:18,875
You are the Avatar,

256
00:13:18,917 --> 00:13:22,709
and therefore,
you are a Firebender.

257
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:27,500
- [inhales, exhales]

258
00:13:27,542 --> 00:13:31,500
- Hmmm, that chakra opened
less like a flowing creek,

259
00:13:31,542 --> 00:13:33,041
and more like a...

260
00:13:33,083 --> 00:13:34,583
burping bison.

261
00:13:34,625 --> 00:13:36,709
- [huge belch]

262
00:13:36,750 --> 00:13:41,458
Tastes like onion and bananas,
but, strangely, something else.

263
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:43,583
Pickles?

264
00:13:43,625 --> 00:13:44,792
- [shrugs "I don't know"]

265
00:13:44,834 --> 00:13:49,792
- ♪

266
00:13:49,834 --> 00:13:52,959
- I'm tired of wearing
this girly disguise.

267
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,208
I don't know how anyone
can fight in this.

268
00:13:55,250 --> 00:13:56,667
- Maybe that's why
it was so easy

269
00:13:56,709 --> 00:14:00,750
to beat the Kyoshi Warriors
and take their clothes.

270
00:14:00,792 --> 00:14:03,417
- How much longer do we have
to serve the Earth King?

271
00:14:03,458 --> 00:14:05,959
If I have to clean up one
more pile of bear poop,

272
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:07,542
I'm gonna throw up.

273
00:14:07,583 --> 00:14:10,500
- Princess Azula promised we
would go back to the Fire Nation

274
00:14:10,542 --> 00:14:12,959
as soon as we captured
the Avatar.

275
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,083
We just have to be patient.
- Shush up!

276
00:14:15,125 --> 00:14:18,208
Do you want the whole palace
to know we're Fire Nation?

277
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:19,959
- Sorry.

278
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:28,208
- ♪

279
00:14:28,250 --> 00:14:29,709
- Good work, girls.

280
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:32,417
I am sure the Dai Li
will deliver the message.

281
00:14:34,458 --> 00:14:37,583
- The fourth chakra
is located in the heart.

282
00:14:37,625 --> 00:14:42,750
It deals with love,
and is blocked by grief.

283
00:14:42,792 --> 00:14:46,375
Lay all your grief
out in front of you.

284
00:14:46,417 --> 00:14:49,417
♪

285
00:14:56,458 --> 00:15:02,500
- ♪

286
00:15:03,542 --> 00:15:10,750
♪

287
00:15:10,792 --> 00:15:14,834
- You have, indeed,
felt a great loss.

288
00:15:14,875 --> 00:15:21,792
But love is a form of energy,
and it swirls all around us.

289
00:15:21,834 --> 00:15:25,875
The Air Nomads' love for you
has not left this world.

290
00:15:25,917 --> 00:15:28,625
It is still inside
of your heart,

291
00:15:28,667 --> 00:15:32,458
and is reborn in
the form of new love.

292
00:15:36,166 --> 00:15:38,500
Let the pain flow away.

293
00:15:40,542 --> 00:15:42,041
Very good.

294
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:45,917
- Can I have some onion-
banana juice, please?

295
00:15:45,959 --> 00:15:48,208
- ♪

296
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:51,333
- The fifth in the chain
is the Sound chakra,

297
00:15:51,375 --> 00:15:53,625
located in the throat.

298
00:15:53,667 --> 00:15:57,959
It deals with truth,
and is blocked by lies--

299
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,625
the ones we tell ourselves.

300
00:16:00,667 --> 00:16:03,709
- Why didn't you tell
us you were the Avatar?

301
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:05,750
- Because I never
wanted to be.

302
00:16:05,792 --> 00:16:08,834
- You cannot lie
about your own nature.

303
00:16:08,875 --> 00:16:12,709
You must accept that
you are the Avatar.

304
00:16:12,750 --> 00:16:15,083
- [inhaling, exhaling]

305
00:16:15,125 --> 00:16:24,709
- ♪

306
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:26,667
- Very good, Aang.

307
00:16:26,709 --> 00:16:30,041
You have opened
the chakra of Truth.

308
00:16:31,875 --> 00:16:35,250
The sixth pool of energy
is the Light chakra,

309
00:16:35,291 --> 00:16:38,375
located in the center
of the forehead.

310
00:16:38,417 --> 00:16:43,291
It deals with insight
and is blocked by illusion.

311
00:16:43,333 --> 00:16:45,542
The greatest illusion
of this world

312
00:16:45,583 --> 00:16:48,709
is the illusion
of separation.

313
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:51,250
Things you think are
separate and different

314
00:16:51,291 --> 00:16:54,041
are actually one
and the same.

315
00:16:54,083 --> 00:16:56,000
- Like the four nations.

316
00:16:56,041 --> 00:17:02,500
- Yes, we are all one people,
but we live as if divided.

317
00:17:02,542 --> 00:17:04,291
- We're all connected.

318
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:06,208
Everything is connected.

319
00:17:06,250 --> 00:17:07,750
- That's right.

320
00:17:07,792 --> 00:17:12,125
Even the separation of the four
elements is an illusion.

321
00:17:12,166 --> 00:17:13,834
If you open your mind,

322
00:17:13,875 --> 00:17:16,583
you will see that all
the elements are one--

323
00:17:16,625 --> 00:17:19,458
four parts of
the same whole.

324
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:22,542
Even metal is just
a part of Earth

325
00:17:22,583 --> 00:17:25,500
that has been purified
and refined.

326
00:17:25,542 --> 00:17:27,917
- ♪

327
00:17:27,959 --> 00:17:30,375
- [inhales, exhales]

328
00:17:30,417 --> 00:17:33,166
- ♪

329
00:17:33,208 --> 00:17:37,834
- [straining]
Come on metal...budge.

330
00:17:37,875 --> 00:17:38,834
- [metal thuds]

331
00:17:38,875 --> 00:17:41,750
- Woo! Toph, you rule!

332
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,166
- What do you say, Momo?

333
00:17:47,208 --> 00:17:49,333
A cup of tea before
we get back to the king?

334
00:17:49,375 --> 00:17:50,667
- [chattering]

335
00:17:53,208 --> 00:17:55,000
- Table for two, please.

336
00:17:55,041 --> 00:17:58,625
- Uncle, I need two jasmine,
one green and one lychee.

337
00:17:58,667 --> 00:18:01,834
- I'm brewing
as fast as I can.

338
00:18:01,875 --> 00:18:04,709
- [dramatic music]

339
00:18:10,083 --> 00:18:12,750
- ♪

340
00:18:12,792 --> 00:18:14,500
- AANG: This is the last
chakra, isn't it?

341
00:18:14,542 --> 00:18:16,291
- GURU:
Yes.

342
00:18:16,333 --> 00:18:18,000
Once you open this chakra,

343
00:18:18,041 --> 00:18:21,875
you will be able go in and out
of the Avatar State at will.

344
00:18:21,917 --> 00:18:23,792
And when you are in
the Avatar State,

345
00:18:23,834 --> 00:18:25,750
you will have
complete control

346
00:18:25,792 --> 00:18:29,291
and awareness
of all your actions.

347
00:18:29,333 --> 00:18:30,834
- Let's do this.

348
00:18:30,875 --> 00:18:34,917
- The Thought chakra is located
at the crown of the head.

349
00:18:34,959 --> 00:18:37,750
It deals with pure
cosmic energy

350
00:18:37,792 --> 00:18:41,166
and is blocked
by earthly attachment.

351
00:18:41,208 --> 00:18:45,166
Meditate on what attaches
you to this world.

352
00:18:45,208 --> 00:18:51,417
- ♪

353
00:18:51,458 --> 00:18:55,750
- Now, let all of
those attachments go.

354
00:18:55,792 --> 00:18:58,333
Let them flow
down the river...

355
00:18:58,375 --> 00:18:59,750
forgotten.

356
00:18:59,792 --> 00:19:02,333
- What? Why would
I let go of Katara?

357
00:19:02,375 --> 00:19:05,208
I...I love her.

358
00:19:05,250 --> 00:19:07,125
- Learn to let her go,

359
00:19:07,166 --> 00:19:09,834
or you cannot let
the pure cosmic energy

360
00:19:09,875 --> 00:19:12,291
flow in from the universe.

361
00:19:12,333 --> 00:19:15,291
- Why would I choose
cosmic energy over Katara?

362
00:19:15,333 --> 00:19:18,250
How could it be a bad thing that
I feel an attachment to her?

363
00:19:18,291 --> 00:19:20,417
Three chakras ago,
that was a good thing.

364
00:19:20,458 --> 00:19:22,917
- You must learn
to let go.

365
00:19:24,959 --> 00:19:27,500
- [panting]

366
00:19:27,542 --> 00:19:28,792
Thank goodness
you're here, Suki.

367
00:19:28,834 --> 00:19:30,834
Something terrible
is going on.

368
00:19:30,875 --> 00:19:32,750
The Fire Nation has
infiltrated the city.

369
00:19:32,792 --> 00:19:34,959
I just saw Prince Zuko
and his uncle!

370
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:37,000
We have to tell
the Earth King right away!

371
00:19:37,041 --> 00:19:40,458
- Oh, don't worry.
I'll be sure to let him know.

372
00:19:40,500 --> 00:19:42,917
- [screeches]

373
00:19:42,959 --> 00:19:45,166
- ♪

374
00:19:45,208 --> 00:19:46,291
- [gasps]

375
00:19:46,333 --> 00:19:47,667
[grunts]

376
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:51,792
- AZULA: So, Zu Zu's
in the city, too.

377
00:19:51,834 --> 00:19:55,208
I think it's time
for a family reunion.

378
00:19:55,250 --> 00:19:56,667
- [chattering]

379
00:19:56,709 --> 00:20:00,000
- I'm sorry, but I can't
let go of Katara.

380
00:20:00,041 --> 00:20:03,500
- Aang, to master
the Avatar State,

381
00:20:03,542 --> 00:20:06,500
you must open
all the chakras.

382
00:20:06,542 --> 00:20:08,333
Surrender yourself.

383
00:20:08,375 --> 00:20:11,083
- Okay, I'll try.

384
00:20:11,125 --> 00:20:15,333
- ♪

385
00:20:15,375 --> 00:20:20,458
- Now, think of your
attachments and let them go.

386
00:20:20,500 --> 00:20:24,083
Let the pure cosmic
energy flow.

387
00:20:24,125 --> 00:20:27,125
♪

388
00:20:34,166 --> 00:20:39,834
- ♪

389
00:20:41,083 --> 00:20:49,500
♪

390
00:20:49,542 --> 00:20:51,667
- KATARA:
[screams]

391
00:20:51,709 --> 00:20:54,250
Let me go!
[straining]

392
00:20:54,291 --> 00:20:59,417
- ♪

393
00:20:59,458 --> 00:21:01,500
- [panting]

394
00:21:01,542 --> 00:21:06,625
- ♪

395
00:21:06,667 --> 00:21:09,583
- [screaming]

396
00:21:09,625 --> 00:21:13,041
Katara is in danger!
I have to go!

397
00:21:13,083 --> 00:21:14,458
- No, Aang!

398
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:17,875
By choosing attachment,
you have locked the chakra!

399
00:21:17,917 --> 00:21:19,834
If you leave now,
you won't be able to

400
00:21:19,875 --> 00:21:22,208
go into the Avatar
State at all!

401
00:21:22,250 --> 00:21:31,417
- ♪

402
00:21:31,458 --> 00:21:33,166
- [metal clangs]

403
00:21:34,834 --> 00:21:37,000
- It's another
one of her tricks.

404
00:21:37,041 --> 00:21:39,250
- There's a giant
hole in the box.

405
00:21:39,291 --> 00:21:40,500
How is that a trick?

406
00:21:40,542 --> 00:21:43,250
- It's not!
It's the real deal!

407
00:21:43,291 --> 00:21:53,041
- ♪

408
00:21:53,083 --> 00:21:55,583
- I am the greatest
Earthbender in the world!

409
00:21:55,625 --> 00:21:58,083
Don't you two dunderheads
ever forget!

410
00:21:58,125 --> 00:22:07,709
- ♪

411
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:12,917
- I'm going to be stuck in here
forever with you, aren't I?

412
00:22:12,959 --> 00:22:15,250
- I have to go
to the bathroom.

413
00:22:15,291 --> 00:22:17,834
- [metal clangs]

414
00:22:17,875 --> 00:22:20,542
- Ready to go knock
some Fire Nation heads?

415
00:22:20,583 --> 00:22:22,542
- You don't know how much
this means to me, Dad.

416
00:22:22,583 --> 00:22:24,208
I'll make you proud,

417
00:22:24,250 --> 00:22:26,917
and I'll finally prove to you
what a great warrior I am.

418
00:22:26,959 --> 00:22:29,834
- Sokka, you don't have
to prove anything to me.

419
00:22:29,875 --> 00:22:31,875
I'm already proud of you,

420
00:22:31,917 --> 00:22:34,208
and I've always known
you were a great warrior.

421
00:22:34,250 --> 00:22:35,667
- Really?

422
00:22:35,709 --> 00:22:37,125
- Why do you think
I trusted you

423
00:22:37,166 --> 00:22:39,166
to look after
our tribe when I left?

424
00:22:39,208 --> 00:22:40,458
♪

425
00:22:50,625 --> 00:22:52,458
- This can't be good news.

426
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:55,500
♪

427
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:05,041
- What is this about?

428
00:23:05,083 --> 00:23:06,667
Your agents show up in
the middle of the night

429
00:23:06,709 --> 00:23:08,041
and drag me down here?

430
00:23:08,083 --> 00:23:10,458
You will not treat
a Kyoshi Warrior this way!

431
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:14,333
- But you are not
a Kyoshi Warrior, are you,

432
00:23:14,375 --> 00:23:16,500
Princess Azula
of the Fire Nation?

433
00:23:16,542 --> 00:23:19,458
- What do you want?
- I want to make a deal.

434
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:22,834
It's time that I regain
control of Ba Sing Se,

435
00:23:22,875 --> 00:23:25,333
and you have
something I need.

436
00:23:25,375 --> 00:23:28,667
- Oh?
- The Earth King's trust.

437
00:23:28,709 --> 00:23:30,959
- Why should I help you?

438
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:34,333
- Because I can get
you the Avatar.

439
00:23:34,375 --> 00:23:36,083
- I'm listening.

440
00:23:41,709 --> 00:23:43,250
- A message from
the royal palace.

441
00:23:45,917 --> 00:23:49,208
- I...I can't
believe it.

442
00:23:49,250 --> 00:23:52,750
- What is it, Uncle?
- Great news!

443
00:23:52,792 --> 00:23:57,208
We've been invited to serve
tea to the Earth King!

444
00:23:57,250 --> 00:24:03,583
♪

445
00:24:03,625 --> 00:24:05,083
- [metal door slams]

446
00:24:05,125 --> 00:24:07,959
- [dramatic music]

447
00:24:18,417 --> 00:24:20,417
- [lapping water]

448
00:24:20,458 --> 00:24:22,583
- APPA: [grunting]
- [squawking]

449
00:24:22,625 --> 00:24:24,917
- So, what kind of
trouble is Katara in?

450
00:24:24,959 --> 00:24:26,125
- I don't know.

451
00:24:26,166 --> 00:24:28,000
In my vision, I just
knew she needed help.

452
00:24:28,041 --> 00:24:30,000
- It would be nice
if your Avatar powers

453
00:24:30,041 --> 00:24:32,542
could be just a little more
specific from time to time.

454
00:24:32,583 --> 00:24:34,917
- [loud rumbling]
- What is that?

455
00:24:34,959 --> 00:24:39,709
♪

456
00:24:39,750 --> 00:24:41,166
- Need a ride?

457
00:24:41,208 --> 00:24:42,291
- [gasping]

458
00:24:42,333 --> 00:24:43,959
- BOTH:
Ohhhh...

459
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,500
- The Earth King
and The Council of Five

460
00:24:46,542 --> 00:24:48,709
do not trust the Dai Li.

461
00:24:48,750 --> 00:24:51,250
They imprisoned
your leader, Long Feng.

462
00:24:51,291 --> 00:24:54,166
Soon they will turn on all
of you and eliminate you.

463
00:24:54,208 --> 00:24:58,542
Seizing power today
is a matter of life and death.

464
00:24:58,583 --> 00:25:01,625
This coup must be
swift and decisive.

465
00:25:01,667 --> 00:25:03,625
The Earth King, and each
of the five generals,

466
00:25:03,667 --> 00:25:05,709
must be taken out,
simultaneously.

467
00:25:05,750 --> 00:25:07,750
Long Feng has placed
you in my command

468
00:25:07,792 --> 00:25:10,000
while we overthrow
the government.

469
00:25:10,041 --> 00:25:13,959
If I sense any disloyalty,
any hesitation,

470
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,959
any weakness at all,

471
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,458
I will snuff it out.

472
00:25:17,500 --> 00:25:20,333
- [dramatic music]

473
00:25:20,375 --> 00:25:22,458
- That is all.

474
00:25:24,542 --> 00:25:26,250
- Nice speech, Azula.

475
00:25:26,291 --> 00:25:29,208
It was pretty and poetic,
but also scary in a good way.

476
00:25:29,250 --> 00:25:32,834
- Yeah, I thought you were gonna
make that one guy pee his pants.

477
00:25:32,875 --> 00:25:34,792
- There are still
a few loose ends--

478
00:25:34,834 --> 00:25:37,875
the Avatar, and my brother
and uncle.

479
00:25:37,917 --> 00:25:40,583
- Many times,
I imagined myself here--

480
00:25:40,625 --> 00:25:43,166
at the threshold
of the palace.

481
00:25:43,208 --> 00:25:46,792
But I always thought I would
be here as a conqueror.

482
00:25:46,834 --> 00:25:50,417
Instead, we are the Earth King's
personal guests,

483
00:25:50,458 --> 00:25:52,583
here to serve him tea.

484
00:25:52,625 --> 00:25:55,333
Destiny is a funny thing.

485
00:25:55,375 --> 00:25:56,834
- It sure is, Uncle.

486
00:25:56,875 --> 00:25:59,834
- TOPH: So, how did it
go with the Guru?

487
00:25:59,875 --> 00:26:01,792
Did you master
the Avatar State?

488
00:26:01,834 --> 00:26:03,208
- Uh...

489
00:26:03,250 --> 00:26:04,875
- If you leave now,

490
00:26:04,917 --> 00:26:07,417
you won't be able to go into
the Avatar State at all!

491
00:26:07,458 --> 00:26:08,458
- SOKKA:
Aang, are you okay?

492
00:26:08,500 --> 00:26:09,875
- I'm great.

493
00:26:09,917 --> 00:26:11,625
It went great
with the Guru.

494
00:26:11,667 --> 00:26:13,709
I completely mastered
the Avatar State.

495
00:26:13,750 --> 00:26:15,291
[self-conscious
laughter]

496
00:26:15,333 --> 00:26:16,917
Yeah.

497
00:26:23,667 --> 00:26:25,834
- What's taking so long?

498
00:26:25,875 --> 00:26:28,667
- Maybe the Earth King
overslept.

499
00:26:32,458 --> 00:26:34,125
- Something's not right.

500
00:26:34,166 --> 00:26:36,458
- ♪

501
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:38,792
- AZULA:
It's tea time.

502
00:26:38,834 --> 00:26:39,667
- Azula!

503
00:26:39,709 --> 00:26:41,417
- Have you met
the Dai Li?

504
00:26:41,458 --> 00:26:42,875
They're Earthbenders,

505
00:26:42,917 --> 00:26:46,458
but they have a killer instinct
that's so Firebender.

506
00:26:46,500 --> 00:26:48,750
I just love it.

507
00:26:48,792 --> 00:26:51,542
- Did I ever tell you
how I got the nickname

508
00:26:51,583 --> 00:26:53,250
the "Dragon of the West"?

509
00:26:53,291 --> 00:26:57,000
- I'm not interested in
a lengthy anecdote, Uncle.

510
00:26:57,041 --> 00:26:59,166
- It's more of
a demonstration, really.

511
00:26:59,208 --> 00:27:00,709
[sipping tea]

512
00:27:00,750 --> 00:27:03,000
- [dramatic music]

513
00:27:03,041 --> 00:27:06,041
♪

514
00:27:13,458 --> 00:27:16,250
- [explosion]

515
00:27:16,291 --> 00:27:17,250
- [screaming]

516
00:27:17,291 --> 00:27:18,959
[grunts]

517
00:27:21,166 --> 00:27:22,500
Come on!

518
00:27:22,542 --> 00:27:24,500
You'll be fine!

519
00:27:24,542 --> 00:27:26,625
- No. I'm tired
of running.

520
00:27:26,667 --> 00:27:28,458
It's time I faced Azula.

521
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:32,792
- ♪

522
00:27:32,834 --> 00:27:34,959
- AZULA:
You're so dramatic.

523
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:37,917
What? Are you going to
challenge me to an Agni Kai?

524
00:27:37,959 --> 00:27:40,166
- Yes! I challenge you!

525
00:27:40,208 --> 00:27:41,458
- No, thanks.

526
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,375
- [roar of effort]

527
00:27:44,417 --> 00:27:48,250
- ♪

528
00:27:48,291 --> 00:27:49,500
- Oh!

529
00:27:49,542 --> 00:27:50,834
[straining]

530
00:27:55,208 --> 00:27:57,083
- APPA:
[growling]

531
00:27:57,125 --> 00:27:58,667
- Katara's fine.

532
00:27:58,709 --> 00:28:00,667
You have nothing
to worry about.

533
00:28:00,709 --> 00:28:02,291
- But, in my vision...

534
00:28:02,333 --> 00:28:04,166
I felt so sure that
she was in trouble.

535
00:28:04,208 --> 00:28:06,208
- Well, she met with
the Council of Generals

536
00:28:06,250 --> 00:28:07,917
to plan the invasion.

537
00:28:07,959 --> 00:28:09,834
And since then she's been
off with your friends,

538
00:28:09,875 --> 00:28:11,583
the Kyoshi Warriors.

539
00:28:11,625 --> 00:28:13,083
- See Aang?
She's with Suki.

540
00:28:13,125 --> 00:28:14,834
They're probably back at
our apartment right now,

541
00:28:14,875 --> 00:28:16,875
talking about
makeup or something.

542
00:28:16,917 --> 00:28:18,959
- Okay, maybe
you're right.

543
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:21,667
- Believe me, if there
was any danger at all,

544
00:28:21,709 --> 00:28:24,834
Bosco's animal
instincts would sense it.

545
00:28:24,875 --> 00:28:27,041
- [sleepy growling]

546
00:28:27,083 --> 00:28:30,667
- ♪

547
00:28:30,709 --> 00:28:33,542
- [loud rumbling]

548
00:28:33,583 --> 00:28:35,542
- You've got company.

549
00:28:35,583 --> 00:28:37,041
- [gasping, grunting]

550
00:28:38,333 --> 00:28:39,375
- Zuko!

551
00:28:39,417 --> 00:28:41,792
- [dramatic music]

552
00:28:41,834 --> 00:28:43,834
- [loud rumbling]

553
00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,792
- Momo!
- [chattering]

554
00:28:57,458 --> 00:28:59,041
- There's no one
else here.

555
00:28:59,083 --> 00:29:01,250
- Katara is in trouble.
I knew it.

556
00:29:01,291 --> 00:29:02,625
- Oh, no.

557
00:29:02,667 --> 00:29:05,500
- Wait, someone's
at the door.

558
00:29:05,542 --> 00:29:06,667
- [knocking on door]

559
00:29:06,709 --> 00:29:08,792
- Actually,
I know who it is.

560
00:29:08,834 --> 00:29:10,583
It's an old friend
of mine.

561
00:29:10,625 --> 00:29:12,333
Glad to see you're okay.

562
00:29:12,375 --> 00:29:13,583
- I need your help.

563
00:29:13,625 --> 00:29:14,834
- AANG &amp; SOKKA:
[gasp]

564
00:29:20,166 --> 00:29:21,875
- [chattering]

565
00:29:21,917 --> 00:29:23,834
- You guys know
each other?

566
00:29:23,875 --> 00:29:26,000
- I met him in the woods
once and knocked him down.

567
00:29:26,041 --> 00:29:28,250
Then he gave me tea
and some very good advice.

568
00:29:28,291 --> 00:29:29,917
- May I come in?

569
00:29:33,208 --> 00:29:36,583
Princess Azula
is here in Ba Sing Se.

570
00:29:36,625 --> 00:29:37,959
- She must have Katara.

571
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:40,667
- She has captured
my nephew, as well.

572
00:29:40,709 --> 00:29:42,500
- Then we'll work together
to fight Azula,

573
00:29:42,542 --> 00:29:43,917
and save Katara and Zuko.

574
00:29:43,959 --> 00:29:47,083
- Whoa, there.
You lost me at, "Zuko".

575
00:29:47,125 --> 00:29:50,375
- I know how you must
feel about my nephew.

576
00:29:50,417 --> 00:29:53,875
But believe me when I tell
you there is good inside him.

577
00:29:53,917 --> 00:29:56,166
- Good inside him
isn't enough.

578
00:29:56,208 --> 00:29:58,583
Why don't you come back when
it's outside him, too, okay?

579
00:29:58,625 --> 00:30:00,709
- Katara's in trouble.

580
00:30:00,750 --> 00:30:02,875
All of Ba Sing Se
is in trouble.

581
00:30:02,917 --> 00:30:05,125
Working together
is our best chance.

582
00:30:05,166 --> 00:30:06,625
- Mmm...

583
00:30:06,667 --> 00:30:09,875
- I brought someone along
who might be able to help us.

584
00:30:14,875 --> 00:30:17,750
- [muffled gasping]

585
00:30:19,125 --> 00:30:21,750
Azula and Long Feng
are plotting a coup.

586
00:30:21,792 --> 00:30:23,458
They're going to over-
throw the Earth King.

587
00:30:23,500 --> 00:30:24,875
- My sister!

588
00:30:24,917 --> 00:30:26,750
Where are they
keeping Katara?

589
00:30:26,792 --> 00:30:28,834
- In the crystal catacombs
of old Ba Sing Se,

590
00:30:28,875 --> 00:30:30,291
deep beneath the palace.

591
00:30:30,333 --> 00:30:32,542
- [dramatic music]

592
00:30:32,583 --> 00:30:34,917
- The movements of all
the generals and the Earth King

593
00:30:34,959 --> 00:30:37,291
have been plotted
out step-by-step.

594
00:30:37,333 --> 00:30:38,750
- Good.

595
00:30:38,792 --> 00:30:41,166
And the Fire Nation Princess
is cooperating?

596
00:30:41,208 --> 00:30:43,667
- Oh, yes, more
than cooperating--

597
00:30:43,709 --> 00:30:45,625
she's really taken charge.

598
00:30:45,667 --> 00:30:47,709
She's terrifying
and inspirational

599
00:30:47,750 --> 00:30:49,375
at the same time.

600
00:30:49,417 --> 00:30:51,250
It's hard to explain.

601
00:30:51,291 --> 00:30:54,959
- ♪

602
00:30:55,000 --> 00:30:58,917
- Why did they throw
you in here?

603
00:30:58,959 --> 00:31:01,041
Oh, wait. Let me guess--
it's a trap,

604
00:31:01,083 --> 00:31:02,709
so that when Aang
shows up to help me,

605
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:03,959
you can finally have him

606
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,750
in your little
Fire Nation clutches.

607
00:31:08,792 --> 00:31:11,000
You're a terrible
person, you know that?

608
00:31:11,041 --> 00:31:13,291
Always following us,
hunting the Avatar,

609
00:31:13,333 --> 00:31:16,458
trying to capture the world's
last hope for peace!

610
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:17,583
But what do you care?

611
00:31:17,625 --> 00:31:19,500
You're the Fire Lord's son.

612
00:31:19,542 --> 00:31:22,875
Spreading war and violence
and hatred is in your blood.

613
00:31:22,917 --> 00:31:24,458
- You don't know what
you're talking about.

614
00:31:24,500 --> 00:31:27,208
- I don't? How dare you!

615
00:31:27,250 --> 00:31:30,458
You have no idea what this
war has put me through.

616
00:31:30,500 --> 00:31:32,041
Me, personally.

617
00:31:32,083 --> 00:31:34,750
The Fire Nation took
my mother away from me.

618
00:31:37,125 --> 00:31:38,333
- I'm sorry.

619
00:31:38,375 --> 00:31:40,250
- [sobbing]

620
00:31:40,291 --> 00:31:42,834
- That's something
we have in common.

621
00:31:46,417 --> 00:31:47,709
- Well, what do ya know?

622
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:50,875
There is an ancient city
down there, but it's deep.

623
00:31:50,917 --> 00:31:54,458
- [loud rumbling]

624
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:55,625
- We should split up.

625
00:31:55,667 --> 00:31:58,000
Aang, you go with Iroh
to look for Katara

626
00:31:58,041 --> 00:31:59,417
and the angry jerk,
no offense.

627
00:31:59,458 --> 00:32:01,000
- None taken.

628
00:32:01,041 --> 00:32:02,333
- And I'll go with Toph

629
00:32:02,375 --> 00:32:04,250
to warn the Earth King
about Azula's coup.

630
00:32:04,291 --> 00:32:13,041
- ♪

631
00:32:13,083 --> 00:32:15,792
- So, Toph thinks you
give pretty good advice--

632
00:32:15,834 --> 00:32:17,291
and great tea.

633
00:32:17,333 --> 00:32:19,750
- The key to both
is proper aging.

634
00:32:19,792 --> 00:32:21,208
What's on your mind?

635
00:32:24,458 --> 00:32:26,625
- Well, I met with this
Guru who was supposed to

636
00:32:26,667 --> 00:32:31,166
help me master the Avatar State,
and control this great power.

637
00:32:31,208 --> 00:32:34,959
But to do it, I had to
let go of someone I love,

638
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:36,834
and I just couldn't.

639
00:32:36,875 --> 00:32:39,667
- Perfection and power
are overrated.

640
00:32:39,709 --> 00:32:43,208
I think you were very wise
to choose happiness and love.

641
00:32:45,709 --> 00:32:48,333
- What happens if we can't
save everyone and beat Azula?

642
00:32:48,375 --> 00:32:52,125
Without the Avatar State,
what if I'm not powerful enough?

643
00:32:52,166 --> 00:32:54,333
- I don't know the answer.

644
00:32:54,375 --> 00:32:58,291
Sometimes life is like
this dark tunnel.

645
00:32:58,333 --> 00:33:02,667
You can't always see the light
at the end of the tunnel,

646
00:33:02,709 --> 00:33:04,917
but if you just
keep moving...

647
00:33:08,166 --> 00:33:10,959
...you will come
to a better place.

648
00:33:18,625 --> 00:33:20,208
- There's General How.

649
00:33:26,083 --> 00:33:29,083
- [dramatic music]

650
00:33:29,125 --> 00:33:30,417
♪

651
00:33:30,458 --> 00:33:32,750
- [straining]

652
00:33:32,792 --> 00:33:34,166
What's going on here?

653
00:33:34,208 --> 00:33:36,250
- You're under
house arrest.

654
00:33:36,291 --> 00:33:38,250
- The coup is
happening right now.

655
00:33:38,291 --> 00:33:40,208
We've gotta warn
the Earth King.

656
00:33:40,250 --> 00:33:43,250
♪

657
00:33:51,542 --> 00:33:52,458
- [screaming]

658
00:33:52,500 --> 00:33:58,125
- ♪

659
00:33:58,166 --> 00:34:00,166
- BOTH:
[screaming]

660
00:34:00,208 --> 00:34:02,625
- Thank goodness
we're in time!

661
00:34:02,667 --> 00:34:04,166
- In time for what?

662
00:34:04,208 --> 00:34:07,709
- Yeah, what are
you in time for...

663
00:34:07,750 --> 00:34:09,542
...cutie?

664
00:34:09,583 --> 00:34:12,542
- Uh, I'm kinda
involved with Suki.

665
00:34:12,583 --> 00:34:14,041
- Who?
[gasps]

666
00:34:15,917 --> 00:34:18,208
- They're not the real
Kyoshi Warriors!

667
00:34:18,250 --> 00:34:19,709
- [gasps]

668
00:34:19,750 --> 00:34:21,125
- Sorry to disappoint you.

669
00:34:21,166 --> 00:34:27,583
- ♪

670
00:34:27,625 --> 00:34:29,375
- [laughing]
- [gasps]

671
00:34:29,417 --> 00:34:32,041
[gasping]

672
00:34:32,083 --> 00:34:35,583
- Oooh, it's like
we're dancing together.

673
00:34:35,625 --> 00:34:38,291
- This fight is over.

674
00:34:38,333 --> 00:34:47,333
- ♪

675
00:34:47,375 --> 00:34:49,291
- Get them all
out of my sight.

676
00:34:49,333 --> 00:34:52,333
♪

677
00:35:02,500 --> 00:35:05,125
- Now comes the part
where I double-cross you.

678
00:35:05,166 --> 00:35:08,000
Dai Li, arrest the Fire
Nation Princess.

679
00:35:10,709 --> 00:35:13,834
I said, arrest her.

680
00:35:13,875 --> 00:35:15,542
What is wrong with you?

681
00:35:15,583 --> 00:35:17,542
- It's because they
haven't made up their minds.

682
00:35:17,583 --> 00:35:20,000
They're waiting to see
how this is going to end.

683
00:35:20,041 --> 00:35:21,583
- What are you
talking about?

684
00:35:21,625 --> 00:35:24,375
- I can see your whole
history in your eyes.

685
00:35:24,417 --> 00:35:27,375
You were born with nothing,
so, you've had to struggle

686
00:35:27,417 --> 00:35:30,333
and connive and claw
your way to power.

687
00:35:30,375 --> 00:35:33,792
But true power,
the divine right to rule,

688
00:35:33,834 --> 00:35:36,250
is something
you're born with.

689
00:35:36,291 --> 00:35:38,291
The fact is, they don't
know which one of us

690
00:35:38,333 --> 00:35:40,458
is going to be sitting
on that throne

691
00:35:40,500 --> 00:35:42,583
and which one is going
to be bowing down.

692
00:35:42,625 --> 00:35:45,375
But I know and you know.

693
00:35:47,500 --> 00:35:48,667
Well?

694
00:35:48,709 --> 00:35:52,625
- [dramatic music]

695
00:35:55,333 --> 00:35:58,083
- You've beaten
me at my own game.

696
00:35:58,125 --> 00:35:59,959
- Don't flatter yourself.

697
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,750
You were never
even a player.

698
00:36:04,125 --> 00:36:06,000
- I'm sorry I yelled
at you before.

699
00:36:06,041 --> 00:36:07,458
- It doesn't matter.

700
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:09,583
- It's just that
for so long now,

701
00:36:09,625 --> 00:36:11,959
whenever I would imagine
the face of the enemy,

702
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,333
it was your face.

703
00:36:13,375 --> 00:36:14,792
- My face.

704
00:36:14,834 --> 00:36:16,375
I see.

705
00:36:16,417 --> 00:36:18,208
- No, no, that's not
what I meant.

706
00:36:18,250 --> 00:36:19,583
- It's okay.

707
00:36:19,625 --> 00:36:21,709
I used to think this
scar marked me.

708
00:36:21,750 --> 00:36:23,667
The mark of
the banished prince,

709
00:36:23,709 --> 00:36:25,792
cursed to chase
the Avatar forever.

710
00:36:25,834 --> 00:36:29,125
But lately, I've realized
I'm free to determine

711
00:36:29,166 --> 00:36:33,417
my own destiny, even if
I'll never be free of my mark.

712
00:36:33,458 --> 00:36:35,500
- Maybe you could
be free of it.

713
00:36:35,542 --> 00:36:38,041
- What?
- I have healing abilities.

714
00:36:38,083 --> 00:36:41,291
- It's a scar.
It can't be healed.

715
00:36:41,333 --> 00:36:45,500
- This is water from the Spirit
Oasis at the North Pole.

716
00:36:45,542 --> 00:36:47,083
It has special properties,

717
00:36:47,125 --> 00:36:50,291
so I've been saving it
for something important.

718
00:36:50,333 --> 00:36:52,333
I don't know if
it would work, but...

719
00:36:52,375 --> 00:36:59,417
♪

720
00:36:59,458 --> 00:37:02,709
- [rocks shattering]

721
00:37:02,750 --> 00:37:04,542
- Aang!

722
00:37:07,083 --> 00:37:09,291
- [dramatic music]

723
00:37:17,917 --> 00:37:19,834
- Aang, I knew you
would come.

724
00:37:19,875 --> 00:37:22,333
- Uncle,
I don't understand.

725
00:37:22,375 --> 00:37:23,709
What are you doing
with the Avatar?

726
00:37:23,750 --> 00:37:25,792
- Saving you.
That's what.

727
00:37:25,834 --> 00:37:28,291
- [groans]
- Zuko, it's time we talked.

728
00:37:28,333 --> 00:37:31,333
Go help your other friends.
We'll catch up with you.

729
00:37:31,375 --> 00:37:40,125
- ♪

730
00:37:40,166 --> 00:37:41,542
- Why, Uncle?

731
00:37:41,583 --> 00:37:44,166
- You are not the man
you used to be, Zuko.

732
00:37:44,208 --> 00:37:46,625
You are stronger and wiser

733
00:37:46,667 --> 00:37:49,333
and freer than
you have ever been.

734
00:37:49,375 --> 00:37:52,834
And now you have come to
the crossroads of your destiny.

735
00:37:52,875 --> 00:37:55,375
It's time for
you to choose.

736
00:37:55,417 --> 00:37:58,166
It's time for you
to choose good.

737
00:37:58,208 --> 00:37:59,917
- [loud rumbling]
- [gasps]

738
00:38:02,834 --> 00:38:05,750
- I expected this kind
of treachery from Uncle,

739
00:38:05,792 --> 00:38:09,792
but Zuko, Prince Zuko,
you're a lot of things,

740
00:38:09,834 --> 00:38:11,875
but you're not
a traitor, are you?

741
00:38:11,917 --> 00:38:13,917
- Release him,
immediately!

742
00:38:13,959 --> 00:38:15,875
- It's not too
late for you, Zuko.

743
00:38:15,917 --> 00:38:18,125
You can still
redeem yourself.

744
00:38:18,166 --> 00:38:21,625
- The kind of redemption
she offers is not for you.

745
00:38:21,667 --> 00:38:24,458
Why don't you let
him decide, Uncle?

746
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:26,041
I need you, Zuko.

747
00:38:26,083 --> 00:38:28,583
I've plotted every
move of this day,

748
00:38:28,625 --> 00:38:31,500
this glorious day in
Fire Nation history,

749
00:38:31,542 --> 00:38:34,166
and the only way
we win is together.

750
00:38:34,208 --> 00:38:37,667
At the end of this day,
you will have your honor back.

751
00:38:37,709 --> 00:38:39,792
You will have
Father's love.

752
00:38:39,834 --> 00:38:42,625
You will have
everything you want.

753
00:38:42,667 --> 00:38:45,500
- Zuko, I am begging you,

754
00:38:45,542 --> 00:38:50,500
look into your heart and see
what it is that you truly want.

755
00:38:50,542 --> 00:38:52,208
- You are free to choose.

756
00:38:52,250 --> 00:38:55,250
♪

757
00:39:05,083 --> 00:39:06,917
- We've gotta find
Sokka and Toph.

758
00:39:07,834 --> 00:39:10,917
- [dramatic music]

759
00:39:10,959 --> 00:39:13,959
♪

760
00:39:21,041 --> 00:39:27,000
♪

761
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,250
♪

