00:39:38,041 --> 00:39:44,000
♪

763
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:53,583
♪

764
00:39:53,625 --> 00:39:54,792
- [gasps]

765
00:39:54,834 --> 00:39:56,166
- [grunt of effort]

766
00:39:56,208 --> 00:40:00,250
- ♪

767
00:40:00,291 --> 00:40:01,959
- [grunts of effort]

768
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:05,166
- See any Dai Li
agents nearby?

769
00:40:05,208 --> 00:40:06,750
- Nope. All clear.

770
00:40:11,208 --> 00:40:12,417
- [metal thudding]

771
00:40:12,458 --> 00:40:13,750
- Let's go!

772
00:40:13,792 --> 00:40:15,208
- I'm not leaving
